name: Greeting Card Making Kit
description:
All supplies needed for 3 consumers and a staff to make 2 greeting cards each. 

Greeting Card Making Kit includes:
8 decorative card stock sheets, cut to size
24 decorative accents & accessories
8 white sheets of card stock
3 glue sticks
1 Greeting Card Making Kit scenario

* decorative paper & accents can differ with each order.

name: Coaster Making Kit
description:
All supplies needed for 3 consumers and a staff to make a 4 set of drink coasters each. 

Coaster Making Kit includes:
16 decorative card stock sheets, cut to size
16 coaster tiles
4 small containers of modge podge
1 Coaster Making Kit scenario

* decorative paper can differ with each order.
